&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="../nullpointerexception"&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/a&gt; — null reference access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="../unsupportedoperationexception"&gt;UnsupportedOperationException&lt;/a&gt; — operation not supported&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="../numberformatexception"&gt;NumberFormatException&lt;/a&gt; — invalid string-to-number conversion&lt;/li&gt;
